{
  "chapter": "036",
  "title": "陈杞世家",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "陈胡公受封奉舜祀",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈胡公满</span>，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞帝舜</span>的后代。当年<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>为平民时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>把自己两个女儿嫁给他，他们居住在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">妫汭</span>，其后代便以此为氏姓，姓<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">妫氏</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>去世后，将<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>传给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>的儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">商均</span>受封建国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夏</span>后之世，他们的封国时断时续。到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周武王</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">克</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>，又寻求<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>的后裔，得到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">妫满</span>，将他封于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈</span>，以奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝舜</span>的祭祀，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈胡公\">胡公（陈胡公）</span>。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "陈国早期世系",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈胡公\">胡公（陈胡公）</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈申公\">申公犀侯（陈申公）</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈申公\">申公（陈申公）</span>去世，其弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈相公\">相公皋羊（陈相公）</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈相公\">相公（陈相公）</span>去世，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈申公\">申公（陈申公）</span>之子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈孝公\">突（陈孝公）</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈孝公\">孝公（陈孝公）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈孝公\">孝公（陈孝公）</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈慎公\">慎公圉戎（陈慎公）</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈慎公\">慎公（陈慎公）</span>在位正值<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周厉王</span>时。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈慎公\">慎公（陈慎公）</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈幽公\">幽公宁（陈幽公）</span>即位。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "幽公时期",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈幽公\">幽公（陈幽公）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十二年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周厉王</span>奔逃至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彘</span>。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "釐公至平公",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十三年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈幽公\">幽公（陈幽公）</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈釐公\">釐公孝（陈釐公）</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈釐公\">釐公（陈釐公）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周宣王</span>即位。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三十六年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈釐公\">釐公（陈釐公）</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈武公\">武公灵（陈武公）</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈武公\">武公（陈武公）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十五年（时长）</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈夷公\">夷公说（陈夷公）</span>即位。这一年，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周幽王</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈夷公\">夷公（陈夷公）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>去世，其弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平公\">平公燮（陈平公）</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平公\">平公（陈平公）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">七年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周幽王</span>被<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">犬戎</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>东迁。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>开始列为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "平公卒文公立",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十三年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平公\">平公（陈平公）</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈文公\">文公圉（陈文公）</span>即位。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "文公时期",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈文公\">文公（陈文公）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元年</span>，娶<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡女</span>，生子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈厉公\">佗（陈厉公）</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈文公\">文公（陈文公）</span>去世，长子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈桓公\">桓公鲍（陈桓公）</span>即位。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "桓公时期",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈桓公\">桓公（陈桓公）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十三年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲁隐公</span>初立。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十六年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>其君<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">州吁</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三十三年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">弑</span>其君<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲁隐公\">隐公（鲁隐公）</span>。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "桓公卒厉公自立",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三十八年</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">正月</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">甲戌</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">己丑</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈桓公\">桓公鲍（陈桓公）</span>去世。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈桓公\">桓公（陈桓公）</span>的弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈厉公\">佗（陈厉公）</span>，其母是<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">蔡</span>国女，所以<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">蔡</span>人为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈厉公\">佗（陈厉公）</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">五父</span>及<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈桓公\">桓公（陈桓公）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈桓公太子免\">免（陈桓公太子免）</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈厉公\">佗（陈厉公）</span>为君，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈厉公\">厉公（陈厉公）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈桓公\">桓公（陈桓公）</span>病中变乱发生，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">国人</span>分散，所以前后两次向诸侯讣告。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "厉公生敬仲完卜筮",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈厉公\">厉公（陈厉公）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二年</span>，生子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈敬仲\">敬仲完（陈敬仲）</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">周太史</span>路过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈厉公</span>请他用<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">周易</span>卜筮，得到<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">观之否</span>卦：\"这叫<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">观国之光</span>，利用宾于<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。这预示着其后代将要代<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>而有国吗？不在此人，应在异国？不在自身，而在他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子孙</span>。若在异国，必定是<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">姜姓</span>。<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">姜姓</span>，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太岳</span>之后。事物不能同时两大，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>衰落，他大概就要兴昌了吧？\""
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "厉公遇弑与兄弟相继",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈厉公\">厉公（陈厉公）</span>娶<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡女</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡女</span>与<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">蔡人</span>私通，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈厉公\">厉公（陈厉公）</span>也屡次到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>国淫乐。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">七年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈厉公\">厉公（陈厉公）</span>从前所<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>的<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈桓公\">桓公（陈桓公）</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈桓公太子免\">免（陈桓公太子免）</span>的三个弟弟，长者叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈利公\">跃（陈利公）</span>，中者叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈庄公\">林（陈庄公）</span>，幼者叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈宣公\">杵臼（陈宣公）</span>，共同指使<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">蔡人</span>以美女引诱<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈厉公\">厉公（陈厉公）</span>，与<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">蔡人</span>共同<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈厉公\">厉公（陈厉公）</span>而<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈利公\">跃（陈利公）</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈利公\">利公（陈利公）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈利公\">利公（陈利公）</span>，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈桓公\">桓公（陈桓公）</span>的儿子。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈利公\">利公（陈利公）</span>在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">五月（时长）</span>去世，立中弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈庄公\">林（陈庄公）</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈庄公\">庄公（陈庄公）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈庄公\">庄公（陈庄公）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">七年（时长）</span>去世，幼弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈宣公\">杵臼（陈宣公）</span>即位，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈宣公\">宣公（陈宣公）</span>。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "宣公时期",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈宣公\">宣公（陈宣公）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚武王</span>去世，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国开始强盛。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十七年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周惠王</span>娶<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈女</span>为后。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "陈完奔齐",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十一年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈宣公\">宣公（陈宣公）</span>后来有嬖姬生子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈穆公\">款（陈穆公）</span>，想要立他为嗣，便<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>其<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈御寇\">御寇（陈御寇）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈御寇\">御寇（陈御寇）</span>素来喜爱<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈厉公\">厉公（陈厉公）</span>之子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈完\">完（陈完）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈完\">完（陈完）</span>害怕灾祸殃及自己，便奔逃到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐桓公</span>想让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈完</span>做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">卿</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈完\">完（陈完）</span>说：\"寄居他国之臣，有幸免于背负重担之役，已蒙君王之恩，不敢担当高位。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐桓公\">桓公（齐桓公）</span>便任命他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">工正</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐懿仲</span>想将女儿嫁给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈敬仲</span>，占卜之，占辞说：\"这叫<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">凤皇</span>双飞，和鸣锵锵。有<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">妫</span>的后代，将育于<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">姜</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">五世（时长）</span>后昌盛，与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">正卿</span>并列。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">八世（时长）</span>以后，无人能与之相比。\""
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "齐桓公过陈",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三十七年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐桓公</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>败；南侵<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">召陵</span>，回师经过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陈大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">辕涛涂</span>厌恶齐军经过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈</span>，诈劝<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>军从东路出境。东路难走，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐桓公\">桓公（齐桓公）</span>大怒，拘执<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>国<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">辕涛涂</span>。这一年，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋献公</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>其<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申生</span>。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "穆公至共公至灵公",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四十五年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈宣公\">宣公（陈宣公）</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈穆公\">款（陈穆公）</span>即位，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈穆公\">穆公（陈穆公）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈穆公\">穆公（陈穆公）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐桓公</span>去世。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十六年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋文公</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">城濮</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>师。这一年，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈穆公\">穆公（陈穆公）</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈共公\">共公朔（陈共公）</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈共公\">共公（陈共公）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">商臣</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">弑</span>其父<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚成王\">成王（楚成王）</span>代立，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚穆王\">穆王（楚穆王）</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十一年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦穆公</span>去世。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十八年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈共公\">共公（陈共公）</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈灵公\">灵公平国（陈灵公）</span>即位。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "灵公初年楚伐陈",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈灵公\">灵公（陈灵公）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚庄王</span>即位。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>议和。"
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "夏徵舒弑灵公",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十四年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈灵公\">灵公（陈灵公）</span>与他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔宁</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">仪行父</span>都与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夏姬</span>私通，三人穿着她的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">衣</span>服在朝上戏谑。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">泄冶</span>进谏说：\"君臣淫乱，百姓怎么效法呢？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈灵公\">灵公（陈灵公）</span>把这话告诉二人，二人请求<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">泄冶</span>，公不加禁止，于是<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">泄冶</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十五年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈灵公\">灵公（陈灵公）</span>与二人在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夏氏</span>家饮酒。公戏谑二人说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：夏徵舒\">徵舒（夏徵舒）</span>长得像你们。\" 二人说：\"也像公。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：夏徵舒\">徵舒（夏徵舒）</span>大怒。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈灵公\">灵公（陈灵公）</span>饮毕出门，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：夏徵舒\">徵舒（夏徵舒）</span>在马厩门埋伏<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">弩</span>箭射<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈灵公\">灵公（陈灵公）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔宁</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">仪行父</span>都奔逃<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈灵公\">灵公（陈灵公）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈成公\">午（陈成公）</span>奔逃<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：夏徵舒\">徵舒（夏徵舒）</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">自立</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈侯</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：夏徵舒\">徵舒（夏徵舒）</span>，原为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>国<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夏姬</span>，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">御叔</span>之妻，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：夏徵舒\">舒（夏徵舒）</span>之母。"
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "楚庄王伐陈立成公",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈成公\">成公（陈成公）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元年</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">冬</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚庄王</span>因<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夏徵舒</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈灵公\">灵公（陈灵公）</span>之故，率<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>。告谕<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>人说：\"不要惊慌，我只<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：夏徵舒\">徵舒（夏徵舒）</span>而已。\" <span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：夏徵舒\">徵舒（夏徵舒）</span>之后，趁机将<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>国设为县而据有，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>都前来祝贺。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申叔时</span>出使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国归来，独不祝贺。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚庄王\">庄王（楚庄王）</span>问其故，他回答说：\"俗语有云，牵<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">牛</span>踩踏他人田地，田主夺他的<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">牛</span>。踏田固然有罪，夺他的<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">牛</span>，不是太过了吗？如今<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：夏徵舒\">徵舒（夏徵舒）</span>为<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">弑</span>君之贼，所以征兵于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，以义<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span>之，事后却占取其地图其利，那么以后凭什么号令<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>呢！因此不祝贺。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚庄王\">庄王（楚庄王）</span>说：\"好。\" 于是从<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>国迎回<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈灵公</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈成公\">午（陈成公）</span>立为君，恢复<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>国如旧，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈成公\">成公（陈成公）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span>读<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">史记</span>读到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>复立<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>时，说：\"贤哉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚庄王</span>！看轻<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">千乘</span>之国而看重一句话。\""
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "成公至哀公",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">八年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚庄王</span>去世。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十九年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>背弃与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>的盟约。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三十年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚共王</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>。这一年，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈成公\">成公（陈成公）</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈哀公\">哀公弱（陈哀公）</span>即位。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>因<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>有丧，罢兵而去。"
    },
    "19": {
      "title": "哀公在位",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈哀公\">哀公（陈哀公）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>，不久又解围而去。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十八年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚公子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚灵王\">围（楚灵王）</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">弑</span>其君<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郏敖</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">自立</span>，为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚灵王\">灵王（楚灵王）</span>。"
    },
    "20": {
      "title": "陈招杀太子楚灭陈",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三十四年（时长）</span>。当初，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈哀公\">哀公（陈哀公）</span>娶<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>女，长姬生<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">悼太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈悼太子师\">师（陈悼太子师）</span>，少姬生<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈偃\">偃（陈偃）</span>。两位嬖<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妾</span>，长妾生<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈留\">留（陈留）</span>，少妾生<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈哀公子胜\">胜（陈哀公子胜）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈留\">留（陈留）</span>受宠于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈哀公\">哀公（陈哀公）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈哀公\">哀公（陈哀公）</span>将他托付给自己的弟弟<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司徒</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈招\">招（陈招）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈哀公\">哀公（陈哀公）</span>生病，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三月</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈招\">招（陈招）</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">悼太子</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈留\">留（陈留）</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈哀公\">哀公（陈哀公）</span>大怒，想<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈招\">招（陈招）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈招\">招（陈招）</span>发兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>守<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈哀公\">哀公（陈哀公）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈哀公\">哀公（陈哀公）</span>自缢<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈招\">招（陈招）</span>最终<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈留\">留（陈留）</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>君。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四月</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>派使者赴<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚灵王</span>听说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>乱，便<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>国使者，派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">公子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚平王\">弃疾（楚平王）</span>发兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>君<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈留\">留（陈留）</span>奔逃<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">九月</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十一月</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>。派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚平王\">弃疾（楚平王）</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚平王\">陈公（楚平王）</span>。"
    },
    "21": {
      "title": "史赵论陈亡",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈招\">招（陈招）</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">悼太子</span>时，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>之子名叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈吴\">吴（陈吴）</span>，出奔<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋平公</span>问<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太史</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：太史赵\">赵（太史赵）</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>就此灭亡了吗？\" 回答说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">颛顼</span>的族裔。<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">陈氏</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国得政之时，才会最终灭亡。自<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">幕</span>到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">瞽瞍</span>，没有人违背天命。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>更以明德增光。到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：虞遂\">遂（虞遂）</span>时，世世守其德。到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈胡公\">胡公（陈胡公）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>赐给姓氏，让他祭祀<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞帝</span>。况且盛德的后裔，必享<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">百世（时长）</span>的祭祀。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">虞</span>氏的世系尚未结束，大概会兴起在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国吧？\""
    },
    "22": {
      "title": "楚平王复立陈惠公",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚灵王</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">五岁（时长）</span>后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚公子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚平王\">弃疾（楚平王）</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">弑</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚灵王\">灵王（楚灵王）</span>代立，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚平王\">平王（楚平王）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚平王\">平王（楚平王）</span>刚即位，想与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>和好，便寻找已故<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈悼太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈悼太子师\">师（陈悼太子师）</span>之子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈吴\">吴（陈吴）</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈侯</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈惠公\">惠公（陈惠公）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈惠公\">惠公（陈惠公）</span>即位后，追溯到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈哀公\">哀公（陈哀公）</span>去世之年作为他的元年，空缺的纪年有<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">五岁（时长）</span>。"
    },
    "23": {
      "title": "惠公时期",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>发生火灾。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十五年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴王僚</span>派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">公子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬阖闾\">光（姬阖闾）</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">胡</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沈</span>而去。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十八年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴王阖闾</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子胥</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郢</span>。这一年，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈惠公\">惠公（陈惠公）</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈怀公\">怀公柳（陈怀公）</span>即位。"
    },
    "24": {
      "title": "怀公遭吴拘留",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈怀公\">怀公（陈怀公）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郢</span>，召<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈侯</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈侯</span>想前往，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>新近得志；<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楚王</span>虽然出亡，与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>有旧交，不可背弃。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈怀公\">怀公（陈怀公）</span>便以病为由推辞<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>又召<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈怀公\">怀公（陈怀公）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈怀公\">怀公（陈怀公）</span>恐惧，前往<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>怨恨他前次不往，扣留他，他最终死于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>于是<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈怀公\">怀公（陈怀公）</span>之子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈湣公\">越（陈湣公）</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈湣公\">湣公（陈湣公）</span>。"
    },
    "25": {
      "title": "湣公时期",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈湣公\">湣公（陈湣公）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span>到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴王夫差</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>三邑而去。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十三年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>又来<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>告急于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚昭王</span>前来救援，军于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">城父</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>师退去。这一年，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚昭王</span>死于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">城父</span>。当时<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十五年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">曹</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十六年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴王夫差</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">艾陵</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>齐师，派人召<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈侯</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陈侯</span>恐惧，前往<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十一年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田常</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">弑</span>其君<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐简公\">简公（齐简公）</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十三年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>的<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白公胜</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">令尹</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子西</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子綦</span>，袭击<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚惠王\">惠王（楚惠王）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：叶公沈诸梁\">叶公（叶公沈诸梁）</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白公胜\">白公（白公胜）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白公胜\">白公（白公胜）</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">自杀</span>。"
    },
    "26": {
      "title": "楚惠王灭陈",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十四年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚惠王</span>复国后，挥兵北<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span>，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈湣公</span>，于是<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>而据有。这一年，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span>去世。"
    },
    "27": {
      "title": "杞东楼公受封",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">杞东楼公</span>，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夏后禹</span>的后裔<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">苗裔</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>时或封或绝。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周武王</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">克</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>，寻求<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>的后裔，得到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞东楼公\">东楼公（杞东楼公）</span>，封他于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">杞</span>，以奉<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">夏后氏</span>祀。"
    },
    "28": {
      "title": "杞国世系",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞东楼公\">东楼公（杞东楼公）</span>生<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞西楼公\">西楼公（杞西楼公）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞西楼公\">西楼公（杞西楼公）</span>生<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞题公\">题公（杞题公）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞题公\">题公（杞题公）</span>生<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞谋娶公\">谋娶公（杞谋娶公）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞谋娶公\">谋娶公（杞谋娶公）</span>在位正值<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周厉王</span>时。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞谋娶公\">谋娶公（杞谋娶公）</span>生<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞武公\">武公（杞武公）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞武公\">武公（杞武公）</span>在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">四十七年（时长）</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞靖公\">靖公（杞靖公）</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞靖公\">靖公（杞靖公）</span>在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十三年（时长）</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞共公\">共公（杞共公）</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞共公\">共公（杞共公）</span>在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">八年（时长）</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞德公\">德公（杞德公）</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞德公\">德公（杞德公）</span>在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十八年（时长）</span>去世，其弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞桓公\">桓公姑容（杞桓公）</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞桓公\">桓公（杞桓公）</span>在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十七年（时长）</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞孝公\">孝公匄（杞孝公）</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞孝公\">孝公（杞孝公）</span>在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十七年（时长）</span>去世，其弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞文公\">文公益姑（杞文公）</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞文公\">文公（杞文公）</span>在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十四年（时长）</span>去世，其弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞平公\">平公郁（杞平公）</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞平公\">平公（杞平公）</span>在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十八年（时长）</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞悼公\">悼公成（杞悼公）</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞悼公\">悼公（杞悼公）</span>在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十二年（时长）</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞隐公\">隐公乞（杞隐公）</span>即位。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">七月</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞隐公\">隐公（杞隐公）</span>之弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞釐公\">遂（杞釐公）</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">弑</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞隐公\">隐公（杞隐公）</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">自立</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞釐公\">釐公（杞釐公）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞釐公\">釐公（杞釐公）</span>在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十九年（时长）</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞湣公\">湣公维（杞湣公）</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞湣公\">湣公（杞湣公）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十五年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚惠王</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十六年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞湣公\">湣公（杞湣公）</span>之弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞哀公\">阏路（杞哀公）</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">弑</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞湣公\">湣公（杞湣公）</span>代立，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞哀公\">哀公（杞哀公）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞哀公\">哀公（杞哀公）</span>在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十年（时长）</span>去世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞湣公\">湣公（杞湣公）</span>之子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞出公\">敕（杞出公）</span>即位，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞出公\">出公（杞出公）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞出公\">出公（杞出公）</span>在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十二年（时长）</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞简公\">简公春（杞简公）</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐简公\">简公（齐简公）</span>在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一年（时长）</span>，即<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚惠王</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四十四年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">杞</span>被<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">杞</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>亡之后又经<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三十四年（时长）</span>才灭。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">杞</span>国弱小，其事不足称述。"
    },
    "29": {
      "title": "古代帝王后裔封国概述",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>的后代，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周武王</span>封于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>，至<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚惠王</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>之，有<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">世家</span>记述。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>的后代，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周武王</span>封于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">杞</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚惠王</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>之，有<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">世家</span>记述。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">契</span>的后代为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>有<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">本纪</span>记述。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>被<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>封其后代于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐湣王</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>之，有<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">世家</span>记述。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">后稷</span>的后代为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦昭王</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>之，有<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">本纪</span>记述。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">皋陶</span>的后代，或封于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">英</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">六</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚穆王</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>之，无谱。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伯夷</span>的后代，到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周武王</span>时复封于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太公望</span>，<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">陈氏</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>之，有<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">世家</span>记述。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伯翳</span>的后代，到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周平王</span>时封为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>之，有<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">本纪</span>记述。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">垂</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">益</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夔</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">龙</span>，其后代不知所封之国，不可考见。以上<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十一人</span>，都是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">唐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">虞</span>之际有功德的名臣；其中<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五人</span>的后代都做了<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">帝王</span>，其余的也成为显赫的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">滕</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">薛</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">驺</span>，是在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夏</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>之间受封的小国，不足列举，不加论述。"
    },
    "30": {
      "title": "春秋小国兼并",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周武王</span>时，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侯伯</span>尚有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千馀人</span>。到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周幽王\">幽（周幽王）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周厉王\">厉（周厉王）</span>之后，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>凭实力<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>伐兼并。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">江</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">黄</span>、<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">胡</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">沈</span>之类的小国，不可胜数，所以未予收录。"
    },
    "31": {
      "title": "太史公论陈杞",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>的德行可称至极了！禅位给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夏</span>，而后世<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">血食</span>者历经<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三代（时长）</span>。到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田常</span>得政于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，最终建国，延续<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">百世（时长）</span>不绝，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">苗裔</span>蕃衍，有土者不乏其人。至于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>的后裔，在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>时就是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">杞</span>，十分微弱，不足列数。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚惠王</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">杞</span>，其后<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">越王句践</span>兴起。"
    },
    "32": {
      "title": "全篇总赞",
      "text": "盛德的祭祀，必及<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">百世（时长）</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>的余烈，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">杞</span>得以继承。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">妫满</span>受封，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞东楼公\">东楼（杞东楼公）</span>继续世系。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：杞哀公\">阏路（杞哀公）</span>篡逆弑君，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夏姬</span>淫乱嬖宠。 两国衰微，或兴或替。 前者被并后者被虏，都亡于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚惠王\">楚惠（楚惠王）</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>勃然兴起，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田和</span>一举吞噬。 <span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">血食</span>绵延不绝，岂非<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">苗裔</span>之余庆？"
    }
  }
}